1. Input
A csv file (make sure the file does not contain any multibyte character,
such as É, Í, etc.)

2. Process
You will be asked to type in:
a) file name, e.g., data.csv
b) column number of text to be analyzed, from 1 to any integer
c) output format, pdf or png

3. Output
The output file will be a wordcloud in pdf or png.
Please note that PDF will be more resizable than PNG.